oai_dc:dc.dc:title: History of Henry County Commands in the Confederate Army
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Lt. Edwin H. Rennolds, Co. K, 5th Tenn. Inf., CSA, wrote this history, of which selected pages - the cover, author image, title page, and four pages honoring the "colored cooks" - are included. The book includes rosters of various Confederate units; enlisted in Henry County, Tenn.
